Rating: 4
Exceptional!!! I closely followed the recipe, except I took the advice of reviewers who (1.) suggested pre-roasting the garlic and (2.) stirring the feta into the hot pasta before adding the other ingredients (makes it so creamy!) and (3.) increasing the basil and adding chili pepper flakes. I did not have time to chill the sauce and let it rest, and it was still fabulous. But when people went back for seconds, they said it was even more delicious, so if you have time, I would suggest that you do not omit this step. Will make this again and again!

